{"tid":206542,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"★誤信「升級」 數萬Android機中毒失財","createTime":"2017-04-18T12:09:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-18T15:27:09.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"56e0772eb2e4e2ecf9b4496e02feee41e69f2505","tid":206542,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T12:09:24.000Z","msg":"4月18日(二)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報綜合報道】通訊網絡供應商中國移動昨宣布，近日發現數萬名Android手機客戶墮進不法分子的圈套，下載帶有病毒的應用程式，造成用戶金錢上的損失。據指，中招的用戶手機會被不法分子操控，連接惡意控制端位址獲取不良內容和目標號碼，並使用客戶話費發送涉及淘寶代刷、賭博等不良內容的多媒體短訊。<br />\n<br />\n中移動公布事件<br />\n中國移動表示，該有毒應用程式偽裝成手機系統升級連結，誘導客戶下載安裝，使用者下載後，將在手機應用列表增加「Google升級設置」或其他類似應用文件，電話就會被不法分子入侵操縱。而自監測到有關程式，該公司總共攔截垃圾多媒體短訊近十萬條，阻斷惡意控制端位址訪問次數達二百萬次。<br />\n<br />\n中國移動提醒，廣大客戶進一步提高個人資訊安全防護意識，不要點擊短訊中的可疑連結，即便是熟人發送的短訊，也要先行確認；不隨意連接陌生WiFi，不輕易提供個人私隱資訊；選擇可信管道下載手機Apps。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170418/00178_017.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20170418%2F00178_017.html&d=UliE8fwpyfwMZiesMcCM7o9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=7d10f8a3\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170418/00178_017.html</a>"},{"pid":"3dc9c62e9bbd4202b91d3fc2f6087b2376bb1beb","tid":206542,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T12:09:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a79723f8cc2b1ef9066cd48d0145df4e181d3250","tid":206542,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T12:11:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7gW2v1J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7gW2v1J.jpg&h=aa80389f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"